    <a href="#work" onclick="w3_close()" class="w3-bar-item w3-button">WORK</a>
    <a href="#pricing" onclick="w3_close()" class="w3-bar-item w3-button">PRICING</a>
    <a href="#contact" onclick="w3_close()" class="w3-bar-item w3-button">CONTACT</a>
  </nav>

  <!-- Header with full-height image -->
  <header class="bgimg-1 w3-display-container w3-grayscale-min" id="home">
    <div class="w3-display-left w3-text-white" style="padding:48px">
      <span class="w3-jumbo w3-hide-small">Protect your digital fortress<br>with LockFortress.</span><br>
      <span class="w3-xxlarge w3-hide-large w3-hide-medium">Protect your digital fortress<br>with
        LockFortress.</span><br>
      <span class="w3-large">The strongest protection for your digital assets.</span>
      <p><a href="http://localhost:3000/"
          class="w3-button w3-white w3-padding-large w3-large w3-margin-top w3-opacity w3-hover-opacity-off">Get
          Started</a>
      </p>
      <p><a href="#docker"
          class="w3-button w3-white w3-padding-large w3-large w3-margin-top w3-opacity w3-hover-opacity-off">Get Docker
          Image</a>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="w3-display-bottomleft w3-text-grey w3-large" style="padding:24px 48px">
      <i class="fa fa-facebook-official w3-hover-opacity"></i>
      <i class="fa fa-instagram w3-hover-opacity"></i>
      <i class="fa fa-snapchat w3-hover-opacity"></i>
      <i class="fa fa-pinterest-p w3-hover-opacity"></i>
      <i class="fa fa-twitter w3-hover-opacity"></i>
      <i class="fa fa-linkedin w3-hover-opacity"></i>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <div class="w3-container" style="padding:128px 16px" id="about">
    <h3 class="w3-center">ABOUT US</h3>
    <p class="w3-center w3-large">Key features of our products</p>
    <div class="w3-row-padding w3-center" style="margin-top:64px">
      <div class="w3-quarter">
        <i class="fa fa-desktop w3-margin-bottom w3-jumbo w3-center"></i>
        <p class="w3-large">On Prem Installation</p>
        <p>Get the docker image from us, spin it up your device/servers of your choice and prevent yourself from any
          data leaks in the future.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="w3-quarter">
        <i class="fa fa-heart w3-margin-bottom w3-jumbo"></i>
        <p class="w3-large">Security</p>
        <p>With us security is not a feature but a necessity.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="w3-quarter">
        <i class="fa fa-diamond w3-margin-bottom w3-jumbo"></i>
        <p class="w3-large">Design</p>
        <p>Easy to navigate and beginner friendly design.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="w3-quarter">
        <i class="fa fa-cog w3-margin-bottom w3-jumbo"></i>
        <p class="w3-large">Customisable</p>
        <p>Open source and highly customisable so that you can use the ecryption of your choice, and generate random
          passwords through your prompts.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    // Modal Image Gallery
    function onClick(element) {
      document.getElementById("img01").src = element.src;
      document.getElementById("modal01").style.display = "block";
      var captionText = document.getElementById("caption");
      captionText.innerHTML = element.alt;
    }


    // Toggle between showing and hiding the sidebar when clicking the menu icon
    var mySidebar = document.getElementById("mySidebar");

    function w3_open() {
      if (mySidebar.style.display === 'block') {
        mySidebar.style.display = 'none';
      } else {
        mySidebar.style.display = 'block';
      }
    }

    // Close the sidebar with the close button
    function w3_close() {
      mySidebar.style.display = "none";
    }
  </script>

</body>

</html>